{"tid":357851,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇同我一樣好似長唔大咁","createTime":"2017-08-13T09:22:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-13T14:33:35.000Z","uid":101024,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dd6c4bdd6672c7c4ff656dd9848911ab41e326ae","tid":357851,"uid":101024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T09:22:55.000Z","msg":"成廿二歲人 成個look仲係個中三學生咁，手又細腳又細 喉核都唔覺有。一直以為可能天生係咁，但上左大學先知完全呢d可能係生長激素唔夠，應該及早去睇醫生。只可惜我同兩老舊時無知，佢地同我自己都冇好好正視呢個問題。<br />\n<br />\n唔知呢家先去睇醫生仲黎唔黎得切呢？如果有又有咩門路呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 得164 cm 同老豆一樣高 蘇都唔洗剃咁滯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a9aec0933c3b3e6a7e699a246828082f6f376d8","tid":357851,"uid":77054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T09:35:45.000Z","msg":"戒j"},{"pid":"e31973442ddba5fe6f261915d2ace91ea26f5e09","tid":357851,"uid":77054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T09:35:57.000Z","msg":"試下"},{"pid":"76620b7cdb710f935cc49408a28411c13fed44d1","tid":357851,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T09:38:41.000Z","msg":"自貼先講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇圖你話你係劉華都冇撚用啦"},{"pid":"283f69020710bc63712d3de61872cffba9f67a25","tid":357851,"uid":117131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T09:49:02.000Z","msg":"一張自拍+手持連登名"},{"pid":"35d429821bfbc06d9cb41c20da2612ba6e220b55","tid":357851,"uid":80107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T10:03:07.000Z","msg":"你以為搭巴士撞頭，日日剃鬚好爽？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aba145216127ef5b72b502ec9ad5d2dc3ddc333","tid":357851,"uid":101024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T14:33:35.000Z","msg":"認真架屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}